{"tid":611661,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"慈善機構用錢係廣告同行政費係咪真係咁錯?","createTime":"2018-03-31T09:04:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T19:42:28.000Z","uid":18521,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e6e2e8fb27a0ddaea238f37279455989de86cfe5","tid":611661,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T09:04:17.000Z","msg":"將80%既錢用係行政/廣告到係咪一定衰過將80%既錢用係實際捐款個到呢?<br />\n<br />\n如果用80%錢係行政/廣告個到可以令到剩係20%既錢達到1000萬，而用20%錢係行政/廣告個到剩係得50萬可以用係捐款到，邊樣係實際操作上更有效率同更有用呢?<br />\n<br />\nTed Link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ted.com/talks/dan_pallotta_the_way_we_think_about_charity_is_dead_wrong?language=zh-tw&amp;utm_campaign=tedspread&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=tedcomshare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ted.com%2Ftalks%2Fdan_pallotta_the_way_we_think_about_charity_is_dead_wrong%3Flanguage%3Dzh-tw%26utm_campaign%3Dtedspread%26utm_medium%3Dreferral%26utm_source%3Dtedcomshare&d=NGHX1sD0FsocOWVjFLgZz7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=92360365\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ted.com/talks/dan_pallotta_the_way_we_think_about_charity_is_dead_wrong?language=zh-tw&amp;utm_campaign=tedspread&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=tedcomshare</a><br />\n<br />\nYouTube:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3kiuBchutbM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3kiuBchutbM&d=NGHX1sD0FsocOWVjFLgZz7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=217e90f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3kiuBchutbM</a><br />\n<br />\n係咪做慈善就唔可以人工高，唔可以打機，唔可以旅行呢?<br />\n<br />\n慈善事業同而家既資本主義社會既觀念太大衝突。資本社會強調既係人工高就高motivation，人工低就hea得就hea，間接地影響一個人既責任感同工作效率。<br />\n<br />\n慈善機構無辦法做到政府咁樣強逼收稅，正因為佢地係非牟利，用自負盈虧既經濟模式係強逼緊D人有商業考慮。如果人工低但做餐死，就吸引唔到人做，吸引人去諗點樣將D工作做得更好，用人工高吸引人才，提高效率，會唔會好好多呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然，貪污、穿櫃桶底個D係犯罪，不在討論範圍之內啦"},{"pid":"548b0f11d64f8be20f16df459c171ee2949c3b91","tid":611661,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T09:11:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1858e1a2af6c2c3f747b1d2bd20e61399b75761","tid":611661,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T09:34:20.000Z","msg":"點解要負皮我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45add4478bd6a14c13bc27d221bbf2e3799d470a","tid":611661,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T10:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f9a4b32d159e596c6f19519a9cef31a850c7a98","tid":611661,"uid":174601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T10:24:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁政府可以高薪開福利局 俾人捐錢<br />\n咁樣個效率仲高。啲人開善慈機構拎黎做樣架姐"},{"pid":"4870504c1f2286c8e55deaf42783800f9d83dd98","tid":611661,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f9a4b32d159e596c6f19519a9cef31a850c7a98","tid":611661,"uid":174601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T10:24:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁政府可以高薪開福利局 俾人捐錢<br />\n咁樣個效率仲高。啲人開善慈機構拎黎做樣架姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T10:26:32.000Z","msg":"政府有福利署<br />\n<br />\n香港政府只係無義務，亦無權代表香港人用錢去幫另一個地區既人"},{"pid":"9b282f1a5c319ac07065aa5e1e7367571ff88e63","tid":611661,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T11:38:05.000Z","msg":"唔係有好多連登仔屌慈善用係行政費到架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無人理我既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2ed7935cb0b549935f4409ed579b89a5bfff24","tid":611661,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T13:59:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5757e1f0fe0491f5b8042c4f13b